				<td colspan="2"><span>Having led raids in tiers 1-4 of POP and some GoD fights for over a year now, I can tell you two things and only two things are responsible for 90% of raid wipes:
<br />

<br />
1) Bad positioning/agro control
<br />
2) Bad targeting
<br />

<br />
Master those two things and you can practically beat anything you fight.</span></td>
